Total Valid Invoices in Dollars 2

·         Drag and Drop Invoice Date from Dimensions in Filter Shelf above the Marks card. Then a Filter Dialog box will pop up.

·        In that Dialog box Select Years --- > Click Next


         ·         In General, Select 2017 --- > Click Apply ---- > Click Ok.

         

 ·         Drag and Drop Invoice Dollars into Text present in Marks card.


·               To Format the number, Click on the Drop down of SUM(Invoice Dollars) in Marks Card.


·                     Format pane will appears in Top left below Toolbar. Click the Drop Down of Numbers ---- > Currency(Custom) ----> Decimal places to Zero.


·                     To Close the Format pane Click the ‘X’ icon.


·         Click on Text present in Marks Card.


·            Edit Label Dialog box will pop up. In That below SUM(Invoice Dollars) type Valid Invoice $ ---- > Click Apply ---- > Click Ok.


·         A visualization appears like below.

·         To Align the view to Center, Right Click on the View ----- > Format


·         Format pane will appear on the Top left side below the Toolbar. In Format Pane, Click Alignment ---> in Default, Click Drop Down of Pane ---- > Horizontal choose Center one or middle one


·     Click the ‘X’ icon near Format alignment to Close the Format pane


·         Then the Final visualization appears like below.
